Class MpAnnotation

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.formats.mpo.MpAnnotation
public final class MpAnnotation extends Object
A class that encapsulates the annotation of a MGI model with MP terms, including PubMed references modifiers, and negation options.
